extends layout

block content
    style.
        .about-card {
            border-radius: 24px;
            background: #ffffff;
        }
        .feature-box {
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            border: 1px solid #e2e8f0 !important;
            background: #f8fafc;
            border-radius: 16px;
        }
        .feature-box:hover {
            background: #ffffff;
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
            border-color: #0f172a !important;
        }
        .icon-circle {
            width: 50px;
            height: 50px;
            background: #0f172a;
            color: white;
            border-radius: 12px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
        }
        .hero-text {
            max-width: 700px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

    .container.mt-5.mb-5
        //- ===== HERO SECTION =====
        .text-center.mb-5.hero-text
            span.badge.bg-primary.bg-opacity-10.text-primary.px-3.py-2.rounded-pill.mb-3.small.fw-bold Our Story
            h1.display-5.fw-bold.mb-3 🔄 ShareLoop
            p.lead.text-muted.fs-4 Share More. Waste Less. Connect Better.

        //- ===== MAIN CONTENT =====
        .row.justify-content-center
            .col-lg-10
                .card.about-card.border-0.shadow-lg
                    .card-body.p-5
                        .row.align-items-center.mb-5
                            .col-md-7
                                h3.fw-bold.mb-3 Our Mission
                                p.text-muted.fs-5.lh-base
                                    | ShareLoop exists to make sharing simple. Instead of buying more, we help people lend, borrow, and exchange items within their community. We're turning neighborhoods into shared libraries.
                            .col-md-5.text-center
                                //- A simple visual placeholder
                                .p-5.bg-light.rounded-circle.d-inline-block
                                    span(style="font-size: 5rem;") 🌍

                        hr.my-5.opacity-10

                        .row.g-4.mb-5
                            .col-md-6
                                .p-4.border-start.border-4.border-danger
                                    h5.fw-bold The Problem
                                    p.text-muted.mb-0
                                        | Many people own items they rarely use (like power tools or camping gear), while others need those same items. This leads to unnecessary spending, cluttered homes, and environmental waste.

                            .col-md-6
                                .p-4.border-start.border-4.border-success
                                    h5.fw-bold Our Solution
                                    p.text-muted.mb-0
                                        | ShareLoop connects people so they can share resources instead of owning everything individually. By facilitating trust, we make borrowing as easy as buying.

                        //- ===== STEPS / ACTIONS =====
                        .bg-light.p-4.rounded-4.mb-5
                            h5.fw-bold.mb-4.text-center What You Can Do
                            .row.g-3
                                .col-md-4
                                    .p-4.feature-box.h-100
                                        .icon-circle 📦
                                        h6.fw-bold List Items
                                        p.small.text-muted.mb-0 Share quality items you no longer use daily and earn community points.

                                .col-md-4
                                    .p-4.feature-box.h-100
                                        .icon-circle 🔄
                                        h6.fw-bold Request & Swap
                                        p.small.text-muted.mb-0 Find exactly what you need nearby. Borrow for a day or swap forever.

                                .col-md-4
                                    .p-4.feature-box.h-100
                                        .icon-circle ⭐
                                        h6.fw-bold Build Trust
                                        p.small.text-muted.mb-0 Our rating system and verified neighbors ensure every exchange is safe.

                        //- ===== VISION =====
                        .text-center.py-4
                            h4.fw-bold Our Vision
                            p.text-muted.mx-auto(style="max-width: 600px;")
                                | We believe in a world where **access matters more than ownership**. ShareLoop aims to build a global network of local communities where resources are shared, not wasted.

                            .mt-5
                                a.btn.btn-dark.btn-lg.px-5.rounded-pill.fw-bold.shadow-sm(href="/register") Join the Movement






